In this episode of Brotherhood (Ring of Fire), a new group of extraordinary gentlemen assemble once more to share stories and experiences from their diverse lives. These men of faith bare it all and narrate their individual journeys through the path of living for a higher calling. The Five Men of Faith;  Lynxxx, Jimmy, Lanre, Fela and Kola form the Ring of Fire and talk ”Faith”. Watch the video: The post WATCH Lynxx, Jimmy Odukoya, Fela Durotoye, Lanre Olushola & Kola Oyeneyin share their Stories in Brotherhood – The Five Men Of Faith appeared first on BellaNaija – Showcasing Africa to the world. Read today!. Source: Bella Naija